      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm selling my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-cared for over the years. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend adventures. I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home, so feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
