    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the high-revving S54 platform. It features the legendary 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive rod bearing service and a DrVanos solenoid overhaul. To ensure chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been reinforced with steel plates, addressing the common floor pan fatigue associated with this chassis. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the performance envelope remains intact with a factory limited-slip differential and refreshed polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in response. A purist-spec machine ready for the apex.",
